And when you put the new string with the name "Licence" you put the value PS-FAQ2S-KCVE7-3JWEA-YNUK5-X57S9-D25YZ and that's it. The program must be closed and when you're finished here, just close regedit and open the program. In the Overview says "REGISTERED"
